metadata.name: Glitched Peony
metadata.description:
Unintentionally glitched photo from a Peony.

Sometimes magic happens unintentionally and a new artwork unfold itself in front of you.  
Entirely random a short-lived fault accidentally caused this photo to become a totally different artwork.  
The photo shifted away from its ordinary form.  
We are used to seeing and expecting perfection.  
But in a world full of technology glitches and crashes as a result of system errors often occur.  
A glitch within an artwork is somehow disturbing to our senses.  
The art is not perfect anymore but it sure does catch the attention of the viewer.
